<subSubSection type="description">
<paragraph box="[961,1871,1575,1799]" pageId="18" pageNumber="271" type="mainText">Plants succulent; stems often articulate. Leaves reduced. Flowers usually in groups of 3 sunken into cavities in the axis of spiciform inflorescences; perianth often 2-4-lobed; embryo annular or curved, rarely straight.</paragraph>
